title: List of Hyderabad cricketers (Pakistan)
text: This is a list of cricketers who have played <a href="first-class%20cricket">first-class</a>, <a href="List%20A%20cricket">List A</a> or <a href="Twenty20">Twenty20</a> matches for <a href="Hyderabad%20cricket%20team%20%28Pakistan%29">Hyderabad cricket team</a> in Pakistan. The team played 184 first-class matches between 1958 and 2015, 30 List A matches between 1985 and 2016, and 5 Twenty20 matches in 2015.
